{"tid":1698104,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)美國恐怖故事 第1-2季","createTime":"2019-11-07T09:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T16:55:44.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89634dcf0397de66fb3d4afedcb330cfcbef6cb7","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=73c4450a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=e5fb0893\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=88c0130e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/5fbf50143124def779d4905e1a424b56\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F5fbf50143124def779d4905e1a424b56&h=cdf757fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nbKGmkYirdM/US8bvyFvQHI/AAAAAAAAC2s/PvNbzuxVwu4/s1600/American-Horror-Story-Asylum-S2-Poster-2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-nbKGmkYirdM%2FUS8bvyFvQHI%2FAAAAAAAAC2s%2FPvNbzuxVwu4%2Fs1600%2FAmerican-Horror-Story-Asylum-S2-Poster-2.jpeg&h=8b80372e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事發生在2011年的哈蒙一家－精神科醫師班（迪倫&middot;麥狄蒙）、妻子薇薇安（康妮&middot;布里登）以及他們十七歲的女兒紫羅蘭（泰莎&middot;法蜜嘉），係因班在薇薇安流產休養期間，和自己的學生發生婚外情曝光，為了拯救破碎婚姻，一家遠從波士頓搬至洛杉磯，開始新生活。 哈蒙一家入住這棟以當地極低價格買下的豪宅後，結識了其鄰居亦為該豪宅前屋主的蘭登一家－婦人康絲坦絲（潔西卡&middot;蘭芝）和她的兩個孩子－泰特（伊凡&middot;彼得斯）和亞蒂（潔咪&middot;布魯爾）；以及毀容怪人賴瑞&middot;哈維（丹尼斯&middot;歐海爾）。 期間，班和薇薇安不斷試圖修復他們之間的關係，而有著輕微抑鬱症的女兒小紫，在泰特身上找到了能夠讓她倚靠的溫暖臂膀。 不久後，他們發現蘭登一家和賴瑞經常打擾一家子的生活，房子似乎也隱約著透露著某種訊息 ，最後，哈蒙一家發現，原來數十年來的屋主、房客們從來沒離開過... <br />\n<br />\n2.此為美國恐怖故事播出之第二季，總篇名《瘋人院》，以「理智」為主軸。<br />\n故事發生在美國的60年代，1964年。講述新英格蘭區的一間療養院「荊棘崖 Briarcliff」裡所發生的光怪陸離的事件。荊棘崖裡只有三種人－醫療人員（醫生和護士）、神職人員（神父與修女）以及精神病患（罪犯）。偌大的療養院運作由嚴峻冷酷的修女茱德（潔西卡&middot;蘭芝）和她的門生瑪莉&middot;尤妮絲（莉莉&middot;拉貝），以及療養院創始人，亦為主教的提摩西&middot;霍華德（喬瑟夫&middot;范恩斯）共同負責。而在院內治癒患者的醫生包括－精神科醫生．奧利佛&middot;崔德森（沙查&middot;昆圖）和殘暴的科學家兼主治醫生亞瑟&middot;亞登（詹姆斯&middot;克倫威爾）。眾多病患中，亦不乏宣稱入院是遭到冤枉的，包含女同性戀記者拉娜&middot;溫特絲（莎拉&middot;保羅森）、遭指控為連續殺人兇手的基特&middot;沃克（伊凡&middot;彼得斯）、性成癮症花痴雪莉（克蘿伊&middot;塞凡妮）以及涉嫌殺害繼父母的少女兇手葛蕾絲&middot;伯特蘭（麗茲&middot;布羅歇蕾）。入住「荊棘崖」的患者們經常能感受到超自然現象和科學的影響，其中包括惡魔附身和外星人劫持人類等事件。 <br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=96150806\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=202c72bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92af91c0943a7df97103c287193cd590eca45cb4","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b0982b4e7fc8d2771c4bb8a2779900340047ef","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7086689fb5a58c5f6828c2ce89f272da958534d6","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c06e99d2a31d8ab8855993dea7db2194ebe78e","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebe3376bb251126f06022752ce46a0085a7ae74","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98255332c079e203c56c84253087155ca5ba966","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d235e165d9d75e6cda43fc3bba618f3d40382da","tid":1698104,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}